WEBVTT

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:13.708
But...

00:00:14.167 --> 00:00:18.333
If I'd known this would happen,
I wish you'd stayed cold to me.

00:00:19.583 --> 00:00:20.958
If you had,

00:00:21.292 --> 00:00:24.292
I wouldn't have realized
my feelings for you...

00:00:24.292 --> 00:00:27.500
Or been sad to learn
about Asuna...

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:32.708
Or fallen in love with
Kirito instead of you!

00:00:38.167 --> 00:00:39.708
I'm sorry.

00:00:47.792 --> 00:00:50.333
Just... leave me alone...

00:00:55.625 --> 00:01:01.083
<i>The feelings I've hidden</i>
<i>are crying out in pain</i>

00:01:01.083 --> 00:01:06.542
<i>Holding a sure promise in my hand</i>

00:01:16.833 --> 00:01:27.125
<i>Seeking only a miracle, I wander</i>
<i>through an endless darkness</i>

00:01:27.250 --> 00:01:37.833
<i>If I stay here, I won't</i>
<i>ever see the future again</i>

00:01:37.917 --> 00:01:43.167
<i>Tonight the moon summons me again.</i>
<i>Though I still cannot speak,</i>

00:01:43.167 --> 00:01:46.917
<i>I keep crying out in my heart</i>

00:01:48.042 --> 00:01:53.292
<i>My hidden feelings</i>
<i>are crying out in pain</i>

00:01:53.417 --> 00:01:58.375
<i>Holding a sure promise in my hand</i>

00:01:58.625 --> 00:02:04.208
<i>If I can stay stronger a bit longer,</i>

00:02:04.208 --> 00:02:10.250
<i>I will go beyond</i>
<i>this sky right in front of me</i>

00:02:12.042 --> 00:02:18.583
<i>I will reach out towards</i>
<i>the future ahead of me</i>

00:02:24.042 --> 00:02:28.000
"Bonds"

00:02:35.542 --> 00:02:41.792
<i>Ever since then, I couldn't make sense</i>
<i>of the distance I felt from my family.</i>

00:02:43.875 --> 00:02:47.542
<i>"I'm not a true child of this family."</i>

00:02:48.833 --> 00:02:52.083
<i>I learned this when I was ten.</i>

00:02:59.958 --> 00:03:02.333
<i>"Who is she really?"</i>

00:03:03.042 --> 00:03:06.833
<i>"Can I honestly say I know her?"</i>

00:03:07.458 --> 00:03:13.500
<i>Maybe that strange feeling of not fitting in was</i>
<i>one of the things that drove me to online gaming.</i>

00:03:14.792 --> 00:03:19.583
<i>An artificial world, where no one really</i>
<i>knows anything about each other.</i>

00:03:20.708 --> 00:03:24.833
<i>I immersed myself</i>
<i>in that comfortable world...</i>

00:03:25.833 --> 00:03:30.292
<i>But my two years in SAO</i>
<i>led me to a certain truth.</i>

00:03:30.958 --> 00:03:35.042
<i>That there's no meaningful difference</i>
<i>between a real and a virtual world.</i>

00:03:35.208 --> 00:03:38.292
<i>It's pointless to ask anyone</i>
<i>who they really are.</i>

00:03:38.833 --> 00:03:43.250
<i>All you can do is accept</i>
<i>and believe in them.</i>

00:03:43.667 --> 00:03:48.208
<i>Because whoever they are in</i>
<i>your mind is their true identity.</i>

00:03:49.708 --> 00:03:53.333
<i>When I returned to the real</i>
<i>world and saw Sugu's face,</i>

00:03:53.333 --> 00:03:56.458
<i>I was happy from the</i>
<i>bottom of my heart.</i>

00:03:56.917 --> 00:04:00.417
<i>I swore I'd try my best</i>
<i>to close the distance</i>

00:04:00.417 --> 00:04:05.208
<i>that had grown between us</i>
<i>over the previous few years.</i>

00:04:08.750 --> 00:04:10.083
<i>But I...</i>

00:04:16.333 --> 00:04:19.167
<i>What can I do for Sugu?</i>

00:04:23.292 --> 00:04:24.292
Sugu?

00:04:24.750 --> 00:04:27.375
I'll wait for you in Arun
on the north terrace.

00:04:39.083 --> 00:04:41.542
After I said such
horrible things...

00:04:41.750 --> 00:04:44.708
You're really strong, Big Brother.

00:04:45.583 --> 00:04:49.125
But I just can't be that strong...

00:04:50.250 --> 00:04:55.875
Back then, I told you to
do your best, to not give up.

00:04:56.375 --> 00:05:00.042
But now, I can't stop crying.

00:05:26.208 --> 00:05:29.375
But what can I say?

00:05:33.500 --> 00:05:35.083
Leafa!

00:05:37.042 --> 00:05:40.208
I've been looking everywhere
for you, Leafa.

00:05:40.208 --> 00:05:42.667
R-Recon?

00:05:42.667 --> 00:05:47.625
--Didn't the Salamanders catch you?
--I poisoned them all and escaped.

00:05:47.625 --> 00:05:49.125
Poisoned them?

00:05:49.125 --> 00:05:55.500
And then I followed you.
Hey... Where's that Spriggan?

00:05:56.292 --> 00:05:58.167
Well...

00:05:59.250 --> 00:06:02.875
Well, you see...
I said something mean to him...

00:06:03.083 --> 00:06:06.042
Something I shouldn't have said.

00:06:06.042 --> 00:06:08.583
I'm an idiot.

00:06:11.083 --> 00:06:13.917
I'm sorry for saying weird stuff.

00:06:15.458 --> 00:06:20.792
I won't be seeing him anymore,
so let's go back to Sylvain.

00:06:21.208 --> 00:06:22.500
Leafa...

00:06:24.708 --> 00:06:25.792
Leafa!

00:06:27.167 --> 00:06:29.042
You can't cry, Leafa!

00:06:29.417 --> 00:06:31.042
Wh-What?

00:06:31.292 --> 00:06:34.250
If you aren't smiling,
you aren't really Leafa.

00:06:34.250 --> 00:06:40.667
I... I'll always stay with you! I'll never
leave you alone, here or in the real world!

00:06:40.667 --> 00:06:43.958
--Wai--
--I-I... Leafa...

00:06:43.958 --> 00:06:46.333
Suguha, I like you!

00:06:47.750 --> 00:06:48.750
Um...

00:06:49.792 --> 00:06:52.292
Wait! What are you doing?

00:06:57.500 --> 00:07:00.458
--A-Are you okay?
--Ow...

00:07:01.917 --> 00:07:03.667
It's strange...

00:07:03.875 --> 00:07:09.458
I was positive the only question left was
whether I had the guts to ask you out...

00:07:09.458 --> 00:07:12.208
You really are a moron, aren't you?

00:07:17.375 --> 00:07:20.667
I could learn a thing or two
from you sometimes.

00:07:42.542 --> 00:07:43.833
Hey.

00:07:43.833 --> 00:07:45.042
Here I am.

00:07:45.583 --> 00:07:46.583
Sugu...

00:07:48.542 --> 00:07:51.125
Big Brother, let's have a duel.

00:07:52.667 --> 00:07:54.625
Let's pick up where
we left off that day.

00:08:00.833 --> 00:08:02.917
This time, no handicaps.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:17.958
That's why he seemed so accomplished.

00:08:20.083 --> 00:08:21.333
Here I go!

00:09:23.292 --> 00:09:24.458
Why?

00:09:24.750 --> 00:09:26.083
Why?

00:09:29.708 --> 00:09:36.583
I wanted to apologize to you...
But I didn't know what to say.

00:09:37.625 --> 00:09:40.292
So I thought I'd at least
give you a free shot.

00:09:41.708 --> 00:09:43.167
You did too?

00:09:46.125 --> 00:09:47.208
I'm sorry.

00:09:50.292 --> 00:09:52.042
I am too.

00:09:53.333 --> 00:09:58.583
I still haven't returned from that world,
not in the true sense.

00:09:59.208 --> 00:10:02.042
It hasn't ended. Not yet.

00:10:02.292 --> 00:10:06.292
Until she wakes up,
I'm not really back in reality.

00:10:06.917 --> 00:10:12.833
That's why... I don't know
how I should think of you yet.

00:10:15.708 --> 00:10:17.375
I'll be waiting...

00:10:17.583 --> 00:10:22.208
I'll be waiting for you to
come home to us for real.

00:10:22.917 --> 00:10:26.083
So I'm going to help you!

00:10:34.875 --> 00:10:36.917
Um...

00:10:36.917 --> 00:10:39.625
Wh-What's going on?

00:10:39.625 --> 00:10:41.958
We're raiding the World Tree...

00:10:41.958 --> 00:10:46.292
Him, you, and me;
the three of us.

00:10:46.667 --> 00:10:48.333
A-All right...

00:10:48.333 --> 00:10:50.500
Wait... What?

00:10:50.667 --> 00:10:52.917
Yui, are you here?

00:10:55.792 --> 00:10:57.667
What is it, Daddy?

00:10:57.667 --> 00:11:00.958
Did you learn anything
when we fought the guardians?

00:11:00.958 --> 00:11:06.167
Their individual stats aren't very high.
But there are too many.

00:11:06.167 --> 00:11:10.583
I have to assume completing this quest
was never meant to be possible.

00:11:10.583 --> 00:11:14.833
So together, they add up
to a single, unbeatable boss?

00:11:15.042 --> 00:11:21.708
However, with your skills and EXP, it may be
possible to break through with a burst of speed.

00:11:23.292 --> 00:11:30.000
You guys, I'm sorry to ask, but would
you mind humoring me one last time?

00:11:30.375 --> 00:11:34.083
Somehow, I feel like there
isn't much time left.

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:38.833
I'll do whatever I can.

00:11:39.375 --> 00:11:41.625
And so will he.

00:11:42.875 --> 00:11:46.417
Well, Leafa and I are
joined at the hip anyway.

00:11:46.667 --> 00:11:49.500
--Don't get carried away!
--I'm sorry...

00:11:51.083 --> 00:11:53.000
Let's do our best.

00:12:07.292 --> 00:12:09.542
Thanks, you two.

00:12:10.875 --> 00:12:12.708
I'll take care of the guardians.

00:12:12.875 --> 00:12:16.875
If you only heal me from the rear,
you shouldn't be targeted.

00:12:24.417 --> 00:12:25.750
Let's go.

00:13:07.500 --> 00:13:08.833
Wow...

00:13:08.833 --> 00:13:11.292
But there are too many!

00:13:33.667 --> 00:13:35.583
There's no end to them...

00:13:44.417 --> 00:13:45.917
--Recon!
--Right!

00:13:54.583 --> 00:13:57.917
Wh-Why are they targeting us?

00:13:57.917 --> 00:14:03.083
They're probably given a different targeting
algorithm from the monsters outside.

00:14:03.083 --> 00:14:06.083
If so, there's no point
in dividing our roles.

00:14:09.458 --> 00:14:10.458
Wait!

00:14:11.292 --> 00:14:12.500
Recon?

00:14:13.083 --> 00:14:19.917
Leafa, I don't really understand all this,
but this is important, right?

00:14:21.083 --> 00:14:22.250
It is.

00:14:22.667 --> 00:14:26.458
I don't think it's just
a game. At least not now.

00:14:29.875 --> 00:14:32.583
Then, I'll try something to help!

00:14:34.333 --> 00:14:35.667
R-Recon?

00:14:50.958 --> 00:14:53.083
Y-You idiot!

00:14:53.833 --> 00:14:55.000
Oh no...

00:15:03.625 --> 00:15:07.292
Recon, that's enough... Get outside!

00:15:19.083 --> 00:15:22.042
That's dark magic...

00:15:41.042 --> 00:15:42.750
Self-destruct magic?

00:15:42.917 --> 00:15:46.583
The death penalty for
that is really harsh...

00:15:46.583 --> 00:15:49.250
You're such a fool!

00:16:10.958 --> 00:16:12.125
No...

00:16:18.042 --> 00:16:22.167
No... This is impossible...

00:16:22.500 --> 00:16:23.833
This is just...

00:16:47.250 --> 00:16:48.833
The Sylph Army?

00:16:49.042 --> 00:16:50.208
But why?

00:16:55.583 --> 00:16:56.958
Flying dragons?

00:16:57.125 --> 00:16:59.917
The Cait Sith dragoons?

00:17:03.875 --> 00:17:06.167
Sorry we're late.

00:17:06.292 --> 00:17:07.625
Sorry!

00:17:07.625 --> 00:17:10.833
It took some time to ready our gear.

00:17:12.792 --> 00:17:15.417
Sakuya! Alicia!

00:17:18.750 --> 00:17:22.792
Dragoons, ready breath attack!

00:17:22.792 --> 00:17:26.083
Sylphs, prepare additional offensives!

00:17:27.625 --> 00:17:30.708
Fire Breath... Go!

00:17:38.333 --> 00:17:41.333
Fenrir Storm... Fire!

00:17:48.958 --> 00:17:52.083
Thank you!
Thank you both so much!

00:17:52.083 --> 00:17:56.917
No need to thank us.
We owe that Spriggan quite a lot.

00:17:56.917 --> 00:18:01.917
And we only had enough money
for the raid because of him.

00:18:07.333 --> 00:18:09.417
All forces, charge!

00:18:20.375 --> 00:18:22.583
Don't hesitate! Keep going!

00:18:42.667 --> 00:18:43.750
Sugu...

00:18:48.208 --> 00:18:51.125
--Watch my back!
--Leave it to me.

00:19:03.667 --> 00:19:05.250
Follow them!

00:19:24.875 --> 00:19:26.083
Big Brother!

00:19:47.042 --> 00:19:48.083
Go...

00:19:48.917 --> 00:19:50.542
Go, Big Brother.

00:19:51.417 --> 00:19:53.458
Go!

00:20:12.667 --> 00:20:15.333
Everyone, fall back!
We're withdrawing!

00:20:21.125 --> 00:20:22.292
<i>Fly...</i>

00:20:23.042 --> 00:20:24.667
<i>Fly forever.</i>

00:20:25.292 --> 00:20:27.583
<i>Keep flying through the sky...</i>

00:20:30.833 --> 00:20:33.083
<i>To the core of the world.</i>

00:20:40.208 --> 00:20:41.625
Damn it...

00:20:43.083 --> 00:20:44.917
What's going on here?

00:20:51.417 --> 00:20:53.750
--Yui!
--Yes, Daddy?

00:20:57.208 --> 00:21:03.042
Daddy, this door isn't
locked by a quest flag.

00:21:03.042 --> 00:21:05.833
It's locked by the
system administrators.

00:21:06.375 --> 00:21:08.125
What does that mean?

00:21:08.125 --> 00:21:12.833
Players were never intended
to be able to open this door!

00:21:32.417 --> 00:21:36.208
No, wait... Wasn't that...

00:21:37.667 --> 00:21:39.750
Yui, use this.

00:21:51.208 --> 00:21:53.083
I'm going to transfer the code.

00:22:06.625 --> 00:22:09.875
We're about to be teleported.
Daddy, your hand!

00:22:17.958 --> 00:22:25.042
<i>Higher and higher,</i>
<i>I reach out my arms</i>

00:22:25.042 --> 00:22:34.750
<i>"Surely, surely..."</i>
<i>I'll wish for it once again</i>

00:22:46.125 --> 00:22:52.917
<i>These endless feelings were</i>
<i>swallowed up into my daily life</i>

00:22:53.292 --> 00:23:00.083
<i>Swaying as they</i>
<i>change shape yet again</i>

00:23:00.458 --> 00:23:07.375
<i>Is it too late now? I ask</i>
<i>myself but receive no answer</i>

00:23:07.500 --> 00:23:15.042
<i>It's all up to me now,</i>
<i>both the ending and the beginning</i>

00:23:15.208 --> 00:23:22.125
<i>Higher and higher,</i>
<i>I reach out my arms</i>

00:23:22.125 --> 00:23:29.333
<i>I'm going to spread my wings</i>
<i>and head towards that gentle light</i>

00:23:29.333 --> 00:23:36.750
<i>Carrying the passion</i>
<i>I've lit in my heart</i>

00:23:36.750 --> 00:23:44.958
<i>"Surely, surely..."</i>
<i>I'll wish for it once again</i>

00:23:47.083 --> 00:23:53.195
Next Time: "Gilded Hero."
